title: BOARDWALK / TRANT HEIDELSTAM barks
description: Things Trant says to Mikael near the feld building.

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""Don't worry, Mikael, you'll learn..."
dialogueTree.text: "Don't worry, Mikael, you'll learn all about it."

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""Fifty years ago this place was the..."
dialogueTree.text: "Fifty years ago this place was the heart of innovation."

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""Feld versus Tricentennial -- I wis..."
dialogueTree.text: "Feld versus Tricentennial -- I wish we could've witnessed that, Mikael."

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""On the outside – ruins. But what a..."
dialogueTree.text: "On the outside – ruins. But what are ruins, Mikael? Detritus of lost epochs."

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""We are living in *very* interestin..."
dialogueTree.text: "We are living in *very* interesting times, Mikael."

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""Remind me to give you that collect..."
dialogueTree.text: "Remind me to give you that collection of essays on modern architecture, Mikael."

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""The significance of all *this* is..."
dialogueTree.text: "The significance of all *this* is hard to overestimate."
